data.eml:eml: First faunal inventory of large branchiopods (Crustacea: Branchiopoda) of Western Maharashtra, India with taxonomical and distributional comments

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Padhye, Sameer, Rabet, Nicolas, Ghate, Hemant (2015): First faunal inventory of large branchiopods (Crustacea: Branchiopoda) of Western Maharashtra, India with taxonomical and distributional comments. Zootaxa 3904 (2): 208-222, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3904.2.2
